<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/2114400-will-there-be-an-audiobook-for-dcye">Will there be an audiobook for DCYE?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_2114400'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F54352941-don-t-close-your-eyes">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/2114400-will-there-be-an-audiobook-for-dcye">9 months ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/2114400-will-there-be-an-audiobook-for-dcye">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/68287669-lynessa-layne"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1638469534i/68287669._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/68287669-lynessa-layne">Lynessa Layne</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">An audiobook is an option I&apos;m looking into, just may be tricky finding the right narrator since this is a dual pov between male and female characters.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">An audiobook is an option I'm looking into, just may be tricky finding the right narrator since this is a dual pov between male and female characters. I'll have to find a narrator who doesn't detract from that dynamic. I'd love to have that option available, though.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

