<span id="freeTextContainer9225293334172656065">This is the first in the beginning of a series.<br/>It introduces you to Klive King a man who is wholeheartedly in love with a girl he had met in a lift. He knew immediately that she was the one but didn&apos;t know who she was until now. <br/>The girl is Kinsley who has no idea Klive is the secret Valentine giver. She is at college, mad on exercise and works in a bar part time. She is gorgeous but doesn&apos;t realise lots of men are lusting after her.<br/>Jace is her best friend&apos;s brother who is trying his best to woo</span>
  <span id="freeText9225293334172656065" style="display:none">This is the first in the beginning of a series.<br />It introduces you to Klive King a man who is wholeheartedly in love with a girl he had met in a lift. He knew immediately that she was the one but didn't know who she was until now. <br />The girl is Kinsley who has no idea Klive is the secret Valentine giver. She is at college, mad on exercise and works in a bar part time. She is gorgeous but doesn't realise lots of men are lusting after her.<br />Jace is her best friend's brother who is trying his best to woo her.<br />That's where it ends. It's a great book the characters are interesting. Klive sounds like the ideal man,totally smitten, hard as nails and would do anything for his girl. Can't wait to read on</span>
