        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1052246050" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16217924959009118107">Klive was such an interesting character. He&apos;s ruthless at his business but he has a soft side. A very soft and loving side. A side that would make any woman fall in love with him. After becoming infatuated with a woman he saw once he becomes obsessed. My favorite line in the book was &quot;If I killed her it would remove her f*cking distraction for good, and I wouldn&apos;t have to feel conviction for all the shit I was involved in.&quot; It made me take a double take, was a bit scary, but also made me laugh. </span>
  <span id="freeText16217924959009118107" style="display:none">Klive was such an interesting character. He's ruthless at his business but he has a soft side. A very soft and loving side. A side that would make any woman fall in love with him. After becoming infatuated with a woman he saw once he becomes obsessed. My favorite line in the book was "If I killed her it would remove her f*cking distraction for good, and I wouldn't have to feel conviction for all the shit I was involved in." It made me take a double take, was a bit scary, but also made me laugh. He obviously has it bad. I can't wait to start the next book. If you're looking for a new sexy bad boy Klive is for you!</span>
